{"tid":1707753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(國際戰線)  回應\"火魔法藍絲\"的公關答覆","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:50:37.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a59b892a2bb3a3eee5bd9b8f9f4397226159fd","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"一定會有人問起, 無得冷處理, 不如諗下點答覆仲好<br />\n<br />\n我既建議答案<br />\n- 我都很不希望見到呢類事發生. &nbsp;希望藍絲唔會因此送命.<br />\n- 另一方面, 抗爭者都忍受著不少藍絲暴力, 如咬耳仔, 撞車... 抗爭者抵受藍絲暴力, 完全沒有法治保護.<br />\n- 歸根究底, <strong>最大責任在於香港政府.</strong> &nbsp;特區政府不斷行使制度暴力, 令社會變得不公平不公義. &nbsp;社會愈趨不公平不公義, 自會發生更多暴力事件. &nbsp; &nbsp;故此, 暴力的罪魁禍首是香港政府.<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>如果要停止暴力, 美國要盡快通過《香港人權與民主法案》</strong>; 只有箝制香港政府行使制度暴力, 才能停止暴力. &nbsp;  如果法案不能通過, 暴力不會停止. &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(歡迎其他人俾意見, 集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"b4a03f5b2962673bc6953fefb80a6576e7ebc3d3","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a033768ee7b9a04c1248ce8ccd984286235e98","tid":1707753,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"希望受害者能夠早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得要小心d處理<br />\n政警咁黑人憎就係因為好多官腔式的廢話帶人遊花園"},{"pid":"9caa87a42db2f92ed3fc58fe811597a717479b42","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a033768ee7b9a04c1248ce8ccd984286235e98","tid":1707753,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"希望受害者能夠早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得要小心d處理<br />\n政警咁黑人憎就係因為好多官腔式的廢話帶人遊花園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"多謝手足提供意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795528554bd0e6cdb793282dd6d08d44226e4c49","tid":1707753,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9caa87a42db2f92ed3fc58fe811597a717479b42","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a033768ee7b9a04c1248ce8ccd984286235e98","tid":1707753,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"希望受害者能夠早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得要小心d處理<br />\n政警咁黑人憎就係因為好多官腔式的廢話帶人遊花園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"多謝手足提供意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"呢篇文幾值得睇<br />\n我諗要視乎你面對的對象係咩人<br />\n如果係冇可能接受叔一燒的人的話<br />\n無謂同佢嘈交<br />\n直接認錯將問題問題帶去警察放生藍絲<br />\n令佢覺得叔一燒情有可原<br />\n認錯只係手段 最重要係增加支持者<br />\n<br />\n離開Margaret的辦公室後，那句「你想啱，定想贏」一直縈繞心頭。難道要贏就不用啱？吳靄儀當然不是這意思。所謂「要啱」，不等於你想正確，只表示你想顯得正確，以正確為第一目標，這是執着自我多於追求成功的思維。「想贏」，不是說可靠不正確的手段達到目標，相反，你必須放下我執，時刻修正，不介意認錯，這樣才能找到贏的方法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20191020/20790119/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F20790119%2F&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=cc723437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F20790119%2F&h=1c265c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20191020/20790119/</a>"},{"pid":"78899b7b7bfa857e3f6ac9995917aea031d11585","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795528554bd0e6cdb793282dd6d08d44226e4c49","tid":1707753,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9caa87a42db2f92ed3fc58fe811597a717479b42","tid":1707753,"uid":134071,"like":0,"